728326f-a.title: Richmond: Amboy Road - Swinnerton Street
728326f-a.text:
Amboy Road (foreground, not seen), east side, at about Poillon Ave. The view is southward across the fields of Annadale and shows members of the Staten Island Bird Club on an outing.
April 1925.
P. L. Sperr.
